title: No More Children Please
itunes:title: No More Children Please
description:
Dear Steve and Shirley, I’ve been dating a very handsome and physically fit man for 2 years and we’ve reached a roadblock in our relationship. He’s never been married and he doesn’t have any children. When we met, he was glad I had children because he didn’t want any. He loves my children and treats them well so that made me love him more. I had a child when I was 16 years old and another when I was 17...........................
